data.description: Welcome to this brand new Rehab Cape-Code style home! It has 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. First and upper levels have a stunning New Hardwood floors. Brand new kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Granite countertops and beautiful natural light. Enjoy your meals and relax in the breakfast nook that is connected to the kitchen.  The basement is fully finished, complete with a bathroom. The home has new siding, a new roof, and Vinyl Climate guard windows. New Heater and air conditioner, New, sidewalks and fence. Private parking for up to 2, cars in the back with a sliding gate. Everything is under Chicago code: electricity, plumbing, dry wall etc. Don't miss out on this amazing newly rehabbed house you can call a home. Easy to show; it's under centrilock box.Please use booties located on front entrance. Looking forward to working with you and your clients! Check the low property taxes !!
